		\nDel - Clear Section
		\nCtrl + C - Copy Section
		\nCtrl + X - Cut Section
		\nCtrl + V - Paste Section
		\nCtrl + S - Save to Autosave
		\nCtrl + Left/Right - Shift Selected Note
		\nShift - 4x Speed";

